                                                                                                                        【中国红十字会总会派工作组赴武汉督导防疫工作】2月1日，中国红十字会总会工作组赴武汉督导新冠肺炎疫情防控工作。工作组将按照党中央关于疫情防控工作的部署要求，指导湖北省红十字会、武汉市红十字会做好捐赠款物的接收使用管理工作，确保捐赠款物使用规范高效、公开透明，主动接受社会监督，为一线 ​​​​...<a href="javascript:void(0);" action-type="widget_photoview" action-data="uid=2286908003&amp;mid=4467295461953773&amp;pid=884f7263ly1gbhaw0t61gj20ck0ckgmb" suda-uatrack="key=tblog_fstt&amp;value=pop_butt_home" imagecard="pid=884f7263ly1gbhaw0t61gj20ck0ckgmb"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_img">¡</i>查看图片</a><a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IseF48cgt" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467295461953773:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467295461953773&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a> 【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E9%BB%84%E5%86%88%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%A4%84%E5%88%86%E5%85%9A%E5%91%98%E5%B9%B2%E9%83%A8337%E4%BA%BA%23&amp;from=default">#黄冈处理处分党员干部337人#</a>】湖北省黄冈市市长说，前期我们认知准备都不足，一些干部重视不够作风不实，导致防控工作存在短板和弱项。①医疗救治能力仍然不足②农村的疫情防控也很薄弱。我们诚恳接受、感谢新闻媒体和社会各方面对我们的监督和批评。<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E5%A4%AE%E8%A7%86%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=央视新闻">@央视新闻</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/Ise0kwrzz" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467270207732489:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467270207732489&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a> 【一图了解！新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情最新动态】据2月1日16时03分前各省区卫健委发布的最新数据，目前全国新冠肺炎确诊病例11860例。勤洗手、戴口罩、少外出，不信谣不传谣，<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a>！期待新的一天有更多好消息！<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE%23&amp;from=default">#最新疫情地图#</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a> 【社区、村、物业<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%97%A0%E6%9D%83%E9%98%BB%E6%AD%A2%E6%97%A0%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E8%BF%94%E4%BA%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E8%BF%9B%E7%A4%BE%E5%8C%BA%23&amp;from=default">#无权阻止无症状返京人员进社区#</a>】在今天举行的北京市新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控工作新闻发布会上，北京市政府副秘书长陈蓓表示：再次重申，任何社区、村和物业，在对返京人员体温检测合格后，无权自行阻止其进入社区。（人民网北京频道） ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IscOoyTZB" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467224368318391:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467224368318391&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                <a name="4467220518707681" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/IscIbAxgt?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-01 18:10" date="1580551831000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4467220518707681:fromprofile"> 2月1日 18:10</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6ghA0p" rel="nofollow">搜狗高速浏览器</a>            	            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a> 【好消息来了！<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E9%BB%91%E9%BE%99%E6%B1%9F%E4%B8%A4%E5%90%8D%E7%A1%AE%E8%AF%8A%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%B2%BB%E6%84%88%E5%87%BA%E9%99%A2%23&amp;from=default">#黑龙江两名确诊患者治愈出院#</a>】2月1日，哈尔滨市卫生健康委员会发布消息，哈尔滨市两名新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎确诊患者经过积极科学治疗后，经两次核酸检测和省市专家联合会诊，确认痊愈。可以解除隔离出院。由居住地疾控和社区对患者进行健康管理。<br>1. 姜xx， 49岁 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IscIbAxgt" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467220518707681:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467220518707681&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4467215275172034" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/IsczJlHtU?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-01 17:49" date="1580550581000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4467215275172034:fromprofile"> 2月1日 17:49</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	            </div>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a> 【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%A5%BF%E5%AE%A2%E7%AB%99%E9%98%B2%E6%8E%A7%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E7%B3%BB%E8%B0%A3%E8%A8%80%23&amp;from=default">#北京西客站防控失败系谣言#</a>：设置红外测温仪对出站旅客进行测温】北京西站在出站口设置红外测温仪对出站旅客进行测温，旅客无需停留即可完成测温工作。与此同时，车站对集中到达车次敞口放行，免查验车票，保证在做好疫情防控的同时旅客能够畅通出站。<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%A5%BF%E7%AB%99%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=北京西站官方微博">@北京西站官方微博</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IsczJlHtU" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467215275172034:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467215275172034&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>
